  "title": "Assistant Cook",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Prepare and cook minced meat noodles, soup, and related menu items while maintaining food quality and hygiene standards. Support ingredient preparation, stock management, and daily kitchen operations in a fast-paced environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and cook minced meat noodles, soup, and related menu items to meet company quality and taste standards</li><li>Ensure food presentation consistently meets company guidelines before serving</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the kitchen and stall to comply with food safety standards</li><li>Assist with ingredient preparation and manage stock levels to support smooth daily operations</li><li>Follow food safety and workplace safety guidelines to maintain a safe working environment</li><li>Communicate effectively with team members to coordinate tasks and maintain workflow</li><li>Adapt to shift work including weekends and public holidays as required</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior cooking experience, preferably with minced meat noodles, is preferred but not required as training will be provided</li><li>Ability to learn cooking techniques specific to minced meat noodles</li><li>Ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced kitchen environment</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills to collaborate with colleagues</li></ul>",
